; SAT: Sequential circuit with symbolic input
; Accumulator: acc = acc + inp each step
; Bad: acc == 42 (reachable when inp=42 at step 0)
; Expected: SAT at step 1
1 sort bitvec 8
2 sort bitvec 1
3 zero 1
4 state 1 acc
5 input 1 inp
6 add 1 4 5
7 next 1 4 6
8 init 1 4 3
9 constd 1 42
10 eq 2 4 9
11 bad 10
